name: Basic Dolphin GIF
description:
A combination of several versions of the dolphin: blue, purple, pink, cream, brown, orange, white, black and green. These colors express the emotions and true nature of each dolphin. The description of their character is in the information section of each artwork. 

This time I combined them in a gif to collect all the characters in one piece of art. As usual I'm using vivid colors and I'm trying to use a glitch to add a dramatic effect.
